  "detailed_description": "PomboTroll is an extremely fun 2D game. Fly on the wings of a pigeon and earn points<br>pooping and vomiting on other birds. Challenge other players for a gross battle and be the<br>trollest pigeon of all!<br><br><strong>Goal:</strong><br><br>Fly as far as possible, making a higher score as you get everyone dirty in front of you and<br>win the prize of the biggest troll pigeon of all.<br><br><strong>Single Player:</strong><br><br>In single player mode, you will be alone with the goal of flying far, scoring high! For this you<br>will have to eliminate your enemies by acquiring \"ammunition\" and skills along the way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964170/extras/eaba0ac70d94e8cd01c38221a28d3062.avif?t=1595286828\" width=190 height=190 /></span><br><br><strong>Versus Mode:</strong><br><br>In versus mode, two players compete for \"ammunition\" and skills to have the highest score<br>and the title of the biggest troll pigeon of all.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964170/extras/0a60244a98610012a63476e70eacd770.avif?t=1595286828\" width=400 height=190 /></span><br><br><strong>Control:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964170/extras/b485dc01efe84f0c3ec56a9c4468c4d9.avif?t=1595286828\" width=620 height=208 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "PomboTroll is an extremely fun 2D game. Fly on the wings of a pigeon and earn points<br>pooping and vomiting on other birds. Challenge other players for a gross battle and be the<br>trollest pigeon of all!<br><br><strong>Goal:</strong><br><br>Fly as far as possible, making a higher score as you get everyone dirty in front of you and<br>win the prize of the biggest troll pigeon of all.<br><br><strong>Single Player:</strong><br><br>In single player mode, you will be alone with the goal of flying far, scoring high! For this you<br>will have to eliminate your enemies by acquiring \"ammunition\" and skills along the way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964170/extras/eaba0ac70d94e8cd01c38221a28d3062.avif?t=1595286828\" width=190 height=190 /></span><br><br><strong>Versus Mode:</strong><br><br>In versus mode, two players compete for \"ammunition\" and skills to have the highest score<br>and the title of the biggest troll pigeon of all.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964170/extras/0a60244a98610012a63476e70eacd770.avif?t=1595286828\" width=400 height=190 /></span><br><br><strong>Control:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964170/extras/b485dc01efe84f0c3ec56a9c4468c4d9.avif?t=1595286828\" width=620 height=208 /></span>",
